general: Dear Gemini, you may feel overwhelmed by too many options today as the Moon aligns with the Sun and the nodes of fate. Your emotional and practical thoughts might pull you in opposite directions, making it difficult for you to progress. If the answers are not clear within you, take a step back to meditate or seek advice. In the afternoon, with the alignment of the Moon with Mercury and Venus, seeking wise opinions will be facilitated. Remember that, even when consulting a trusted advisor, it is up to you to draw your own conclusions. With the Moon active in your sign, trust your intuition; it will guide you.
love: Be open to discussion with your partner; communication is key.
work: Take the time to evaluate your options before making important decisions.
health: Listen to your body and do not hesitate to give yourself a break.
advice: Take a moment to center yourself before taking action.
teaser: Too many options? Listen to your heart.
